ns/244402</a>"},{"pid":"5cc74e5f593b7bb52943d35b13a072fc59469993","tid":1486200,"uid":47724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:12:38.000Z","msg":"前排有留意 把聲好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但岩聽既唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U5oIvfraRrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU5oIvfraRrU&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=25b960d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U5oIvfraRrU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XtS3SyevpvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXtS3SyevpvI&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=9332638b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XtS3SyevpvI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JM07F5bYRhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJM07F5bYRhc&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=3739b662\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JM07F5bYRhc</a>"},{"pid":"1bfa27f91128375a5eb8a88aef53af65dc89422c","tid":1486200,"uid":136494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:14:58.000Z","msg":"香港好少人識 Golden hour首首都好好聽"},{"pid":"ed767013fd3946cd987dfc42727d3528afd08502","tid":1486200,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:23:43.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=9d188fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=9d188fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"79eb5963978e3e7109cdf65b89f881c92f358393","tid":1486200,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:10:48.000Z","msg":"Happy and sad at the same time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf24df2720d336a5d2b946b7a8c119b42af3ce0","tid":1486200,"uid":276512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"OMG 好高質<br />\nGolden Hour 同 Same Trailer Different Park 都好正<br />\n雖然佢既音樂唔係啲咩偏鋒同實驗音樂<br />\n但論歌詞既批判性同編曲好多既細節<br />\n都睇到佢既新意同與眾不同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (比起好多主流鄉村音樂)<br />\n<br />\n超鍾意 Golden Hour 融入咗好多唔同音樂元素<br />\nOh, What A World 副歌之後既 banjo<br />\n同埋 Daft Punk 上身咁既 vocoder<br />\n仲有 Slow Burn 好有層次既編曲<br />\n基本上首首都有記憶點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係覺得由 Happy &amp; Sad 開始一連三首有少少失色<br />\n<br />\n佢既音樂高質得黎又好平易近人<br />\n真係值得更多關注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有時覺得好似而家咁樣都可能係好事<br />\n話哂紅咗就有機會會變質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似近排佢只係比以前出名咗少少<br />\n就已經有啲 drama 出現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a24665b5adcfe2601448ad7d625bf57c208c4e","tid":1486200,"uid":298075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf24df2720d336a5d2b946b7a8c119b42af3ce0","tid":1486200,"uid":276512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"OMG 好高質<br />\nGolden Hour 同 Same Trailer Different Park 都好正<br />\n雖然佢既音樂唔係啲咩偏鋒同實驗音樂<br />\n但論歌詞既批判性同編曲好多既細節<br />\n都睇到佢既新意同與眾不同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (比起好多主流鄉村音樂)<br />\n<br />\n超鍾意 Golden Hour 融入咗好多唔同音樂元素<br />\nOh, What A World 副歌之後既 banjo<br />\n同埋 Daft Punk 上身咁既 vocoder<br />\n仲有 Slow Burn 好有層次既編曲<br />\n基本上首首都有記憶點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係覺得由 Happy &amp; Sad 開始一連三首有少少失色<br />